{"tid":2277381,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"果然講古惑無野勁得過中資股","createTime":"2020-11-08T12:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T05:20:57.000Z","uid":40121,"like":165,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"c29109053ee5b96747bf292f7ceb3c68f8635f2e","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係我<span class=\"gold\">三支金流</span>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次為大家帶尼嘅係一個<span class=\"green\">鑽研財報嘅Case</span><br />\n大家可以當偵探小說咁睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時分享下我學到嘅（highlight左嘅）重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對投資有興趣嘅話歡迎尼我個blog睇下上個Case<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">萬國企業 vs Keppel DC</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://3gcashflow.blogspot.com/2020/11/ugfr.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3gcashflow.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F11%2Fugfr.html&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7yIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=27a151e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://3gcashflow.blogspot.com/2020/11/ugfr.html</a><br />\n圖多會分段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇得舒服請善用追故模式或者入blog睇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://3gcashflow.blogspot.com/2020/11/ugfr-trickytricky.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3gcashflow.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F11%2Fugfr-trickytricky.html&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7yIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=87efbbb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://3gcashflow.blogspot.com/2020/11/ugfr-trickytricky.html</a><br />\n事不宜遲馬上去文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------<br />\n警告：今次可能有少少深，要有啲經驗先睇得明，但我儘量淺白咁帶大家走一次我嘅思路<br />\n<br />\n數簿大佬：又比份功課你吖，今次唔洗捉假數，睇下粵豐環保（1381）嘅財務三表，再話我知佢嘅營運有咩特別啦。<br />\n<br />\n今次我醒啦，先去股票網睇睇佢做乜先；<span class=\"orange\">通過股票網嘅公司簡介大約掌握業務，估計佢會有咩收支，對你識別財報異常好有幫助</span>。AASTOCK咁講：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXeZXS1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXeZXS1.png&h=a1245664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁你<span class=\"orange\">可以expect佢主要收入係賣電，然後主要成本係收啲垃圾番尼、維修同折舊等等啦</span>。有概念之後就去披露易搵佢嘅財報出尼睇。今次我無同啲主席糾纏（仲記得keppel DC 果條女，廢話大王尼），直攘去睇佢<span class=\"gold\">分部收益睇佢用咩賺咩人錢</span>：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWWaj6u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWWaj6u.png&h=0a816f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仆你個街，原來收垃圾果下都有錢收咁爽皮。再睇真啲，有兩筆關於BOT嘅收入，加埋佔左成一半營收，到底係咩尼？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bguWfEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbguWfEV.png&h=00c9dd39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n碌落少少佢講埋每個項目嘅毛利率，發現<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>BOT財務收入有100%咁多，這不是無中生有嗎？</ins></span></span>數簿叫我唔洗抽假數，但點睇都有啲奇怪，<span class=\"gold\">一定要搞清楚咩係BOT同埋呢兩筆收入係按咩準則入賬！</span>"},{"pid":"0a462e56b4a7506b90a78a5ae4f3d94df54181b2","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"不過先go thro埋三表先：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DzjdsT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DzjdsT.png&h=2744a880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個損益表基本上係財報界嘅吳彥祖，非常靚仔：<span class=\"orange\">6%管銷比率暗示管理團隊非常有效</span>、<span class=\"gold\">22%淨利率係電廠尼講絕對頂級</span>（中電大約15%），驟眼睇呢間係支那少數養得掂自己嘅電廠，仲有息派，有少少吸引。但未搞清楚咩係BOT收入之前我真係唔敢亂尼。值得留意嘅係<span class=\"orange\">利息支出有啲多，要睇下佢資產負債</span>上有無咩問題。"},{"pid":"9700abdc257fd9000fcfb3df3edf2efecd7557dc","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ed5N6Op.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEd5N6Op.png&h=e3514956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鬼，好撚鬼。<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">無形資產一年之內升左43%，增加左2150MRMB，而物業廠房反而無增加到！</span></span><br />\n發電廠係<span class=\"green\">重資產行業</span>，每年應該都會有一大筆支出用於<span class=\"orange\">維修同建設，呢筆錢會加入物業廠房項目，係來年以折舊形式逐年攤分</span>。<span class=\"gold\">而家物業廠房無增加到，一係佢啲野唔洗維修，一係佢無擴建，完全違反發電行業嘅常理</span>，可疑到我變左小剛眼(-_-)。<br />\n<br />\n最常見嘅無形資產係<span class=\"green\">商譽</span>，一般係<span class=\"gold\">高於賬面價收購公司果陣產生；收購之後，賬面價值嘅物業廠房部份會照入番相應項目，而溢價部份會以商譽記賬</span>。家陣佢突然多左咁多，<span class=\"red\">但物業廠房項不增反退</span>，咁一係佢收購空氣，一係就係其他野大幅增加左，第18號附注絕對係睇撚硬！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wdzMOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wdzMOw.png&h=1107f8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><ins>資產係「啲錢洗左去邊」，負債就係「啲錢邊個出」</ins></strong></span>。對番負債方，無形資產果2150M主要由銀行貸款同應付賬款加埋1328M支持。<span class=\"red\">如果啲無形資產真係無形，咁就係平白增加負債，財務狀況實際上比想象中危！</span>"},{"pid":"20a1225efe3a76f9b4721294de7f1f494823f37b","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pm7gZ9D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpm7gZ9D.png&h=13be458c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電廠嘅損益表一般包含左資產折舊，但因為<span class=\"gold\">折舊唔係現金支出，佢會加番入營業現金流</span>，令營業現金流入高於盈利。我滿心歡喜以為粵豐都會咁，點知無唔止，仲要係<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>流出</ins></span></span>！抬頭一看----果然係咁，<span class=\"gold\">BOT收入根本唔撚係現金收入尼，必需要係現金流量表度減走；同時BOT成本就真係現金流出，所以無加番入現金流報表</span>！屌屌屌欺騙我感情！！！！"},{"pid":"d2a7ed459c33f79d1e099f11b96cce2755288931","tid":2277381,"uid":369192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"善心一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38531485a596e3a1c7eb1c9eb9a9b9b5fc38e577","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"但係<span class=\"orange\">一筆數過得損益表，必然係入左資產負表</span>；<span class=\"gold\">既然唔係入現金項目，必然就係去左其他地方</span>。番頭一睇，BOT收入大約2014M，而無形資產增加2150M，<span class=\"red\">似乎情況就係BOT收入經損益入左無形資產</span>。果然，附注18號咁寫：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt21rQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt21rQg.png&h=05224849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁到底BOT係乜東東尼？點解會咁樣入賬？現金流量表上面有講<span class=\"orange\">「建設-營運-移交 Build-Operate-Transfer」</span>，google一下原來係基建項目嘅公私合作模式之一，有朋友就搵左張咁嘅圖講解埋其他合作模式：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8izMQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8izMQp.jpg&h=96fe9ef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單尼講，<span class=\"gold\"><ins><em>BOT就係私營公司同政府定立合約，由私人公司興建所需設施，然後營運一定年期，約滿後移交政府；而私人企業付出嘅建造同營運嘅成本就係營運期間賺番番尼</em></ins></span>；呢個模式係香港都有著名例子----閪隧。"},{"pid":"a30e13a1ff03d0a0b47575ab09750a3bf355d817","tid":2277381,"uid":27072,"like":1,"dislike":53,"score":-52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"財報:支牛專有名詞  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b150a8260cad178c64b8dc1cf127556cee9f674","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"番番尼粵豐，咁點解明明係<span class=\"red\">興建成本，理應係放入資本資出</span>唔經損益表，點解而家又放係度？呢個時候睇番佢個會計政策：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh7s6Q5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh7s6Q5.png&h=09cf35c0&s={SIZE}\" /> 姐係話<span class=\"gold\">粵豐起棟野其實係收費嘅，而個收益係起果下就因為履行左義務而成為應計收入</span>。咁但舊錢幾時先收得番？仆你個街，我摷到去上巿文件嘅會計政策先搵到：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NtzMRg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NtzMRg.png&h=6ef0bc0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姐係話，到<span class=\"green\">楝野投產果陣，收番尼嘅垃圾處理現金收入</span>會分做兩部份，<span class=\"orange\">一部份入損益確認為收入</span>，另一部份會用尼<span class=\"gold\">沖銷建造收入造成嘅無形資產，將呢個數撥番去現金項目</span>。<br />\n<br />\n好快咁recap一次：<span class=\"gold\"><em><ins>由於興建之際已經履行左合約義務，因此興建收益同成本都會記入損益，以無形資產形式儲存起來；到廠房投入營運後收入嘅一部份就照計做收入</ins></em></span>，<span class=\"red\">另一部份用尼沖銷筆無形資產去實現（來自遙遠過去嘅）盈利</span>。<br />\n<br />\n睇明左啲數之後，我就覺得現金流量表要做少少調整。我地而家知道銷售成本入面<span class=\"orange\">「BOT建設成本」係用尼起啲廠，啲廠第日係經營期入面會有產出，所以呢筆成本應該計成資本支出</span>，加番落CFO（營運現金流），然後係CFI（投資現金流）度先減，咁先反映到佢收<span class=\"orange\">垃圾發電（本業）帶來嘅現金流入</span>以及<span class=\"gold\">起多啲廠帶來嘅現金流出</span>。而係損益表嘅<span class=\"red\">建造收益扣除成本後，然後入賬應收款項，唔係計入無形資產</span>，咁成件事就會清楚好多。<br />\n<br />\n數簿：無錯啦，1381主要想帶出嘅訊息係，<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins>損益表一定要配住現金流尼睇，唔係可能會比未實現盈利誤導左架啦！</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"06dfb7159e731d97ca8e73d3b8292146d4405ee3","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"a30e13a1ff03d0a0b47575ab09750a3bf355d817","tid":2277381,"uid":27072,"like":1,"dislike":53,"score":-52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"財報:支牛專有名詞  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"台灣人都係叫財報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWhT2r8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWhT2r8.png&h=ad5bf47f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77ebf989b6e0491819b209bf3dfd3682ff7c25f4","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d2a7ed459c33f79d1e099f11b96cce2755288931","tid":2277381,"uid":369192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"善心一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"感謝野生嘅野生絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4bbb317cc26fa007cd79d20bff4f9eaa715b44","tid":2277381,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"香港以前啲隧道不嬲都係用BTO<br />\n紅東西隧 大老山大欖都係<br />\n西隧只係算後期嘅一個例子<br />\n紅隧 東隧 大老山已經被政府收翻<br />\n大欖同西隧𠵱幾年都會完"},{"pid":"5bed340fcfba6e981cec93e9a264e0501869dce1","tid":2277381,"uid":40121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"